{"tid":1629802,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"荃灣綫列車轉軌時衝燈出軌撞杆 全綫停駛","createTime":"2019-10-06T10:32:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T11:42:04.000Z","uid":23707,"like":35,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"9a45db10f0f77762c7f7b51fd1068fe8f7202f26","tid":1629802,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T10:32:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yYm0PMY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyYm0PMY.png&h=a0326155&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"02608513f3034ef20214567749d0abd88612bfde","tid":1629802,"uid":23707,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T10:34:56.000Z","msg":"荃灣綫今日多個車站關閉，只提供局部服務，下午港鐵再宣佈油麻地及荔枝角站關閉。至傍晚6時，荃灣綫一列往美孚方向列車更懷疑發生嚴重事故，令荃灣綫來回方向列車服務暫停。<br />\n<br />\n有乘客向《蘋果》表示，當時車上有多名乘客，列車駛至茘景站附近，突然傳出「嘭」一聲巨響，車廂內的燈熄了一大半，有人失足跌倒在地上，多人受傷，有人驚慌尖叫，現場一片混亂。大批救護員及消防到場協助疏散，據悉有3人受傷不適。<br />\n<br />\n消息指，列車前往茘景站下行月台接載乘客，疑經中間車道轉軌往美孚站上行月台時，衝燈出軌，車頭位置撞到防撞杆。"},{"pid":"fd4ad4c253a116d35633b93e2294e3cfceb91002","tid":1629802,"uid":126053,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T10:35:25.000Z","msg":"不合作運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aff56cb03446ab6a5426d2767b623aa262515f27","tid":1629802,"uid":293677,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T10:35:26.000Z","msg":"黨鐵真炒車"},{"pid":"c70c739bf355da4b6f118dd6af183a3c59dbd0fd","tid":1629802,"uid":193233,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T10:35:39.000Z","msg":"自炒？"},{"pid":"62aa7e44aa6c63213784375432329f1bcf2345f9","tid":1629802,"uid":60924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c70c739bf355da4b6f118dd6af183a3c59dbd0fd","tid":1629802,"uid":193233,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T10:35:39.000Z","msg":"自炒？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T10:36:20.000Z","msg":"YES"},{"pid":"a20b9c64ac6ea85c77386ebee272cab4f9e2f7e9","tid":1629802,"uid":228582,"like":0,"di